nodes.text: Starliner was a street in Coronet City. In 18 ABY, during the First Corellian Insurrection, Han Solo and Belindi Kalenda met where Starliner crossed Volbick in an attempt to steal a spaceship.
It is unknown whether Starliner and Starline Avenue, both of which are first mentioned in Ambush at Corellia, refer to the same street.
